<https://www.gov.uk/government/people/darren-jones> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "The Rt Hon Darren Jones MP was appointed Chancellor of the Duchy of Lancaster on 5 September 2025, Minister for Intergovernmental Relations on 6 September 2025 and Chief Secretary to the Prime Minister at the Cabinet Office on 1 September 2025. He was previously Chief Secretary to the Treasury. He was elected as the MP for Bristol North West in June 2017."@en .
